#

Chipotle Honey Lime Chicken Tacos

$15.99
600 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten Free

Tags:

TacosChickenSpicyQuickEasy

Description

Zesty and flavorful chicken tacos with a sweet and spicy twist, served with fresh toppings.

Ingredients

  • Chicken Thighs: 1 lb
  • Chipotle Peppers in Adobo Sauce: 2
  • Honey: 3 tbsp
  • Lime Juice: 2 tbsp
  • Corn Tortillas: 8
  • Cabbage (shredded): 1 cup
  • Cilantro (chopped): 1/4 cup
  • Avocado (sliced): 1
  • Sour Cream: 1/2 cup
